value.name: Manabi Straight!
value.original_name: がくえんゆーとぴあ まなびストレート！
value.overview: The year is 2035 and schools have been suffering due to declining birthrate, having forced many of them to close. An energetic girl named Manami Amamiya transfers to a new school where she quickly becomes the student council president and starts to bring back vigor in the students' lives.
